Operations & sequences
1.Test all operations.
	AND
	OR
	ADD
	SUB
	Carry
	Overflow
	Zero
	Negative
	
	results for extreme argument values

	error handling in data transmission
	ERR_DATA = incorrect input data
	ERR_CRC = bad CRC for the input data
	ERR_OP = unknown ALU operation code


2.Execute all operations after reset.
3.Execute reset after all operations.
4.Run multiply after a single-cycle operation.
5.Run single cycle operation after multiply.
6.Simulate all operations twice in a row.

B.Specific data corners
1.Simulate all zeros on an input for all operations.
2.Simulate all ones on an input for all operations
